text: Benthoclionella is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Clavatulidae. ==Species== Species within the genus Benthoclionella include: * Benthoclionella jenneri Kilburn, 1974 ==References== * Kilburn R.N. (1974). Taxonomic notes on South African marine Mollusca (3): Gastropoda: Prosobranchia, with descriptions of new taxa of Naticidae, Fasciolariidae, Magilidae, Volutomitridae and Turridae. Annals of the Natal Museum. 22: 187-220. ==External links== Category:Clavatulidae Category:Monotypic gastropod genera
title: Benthoclionella
